    * Revert "add lifespan"

    This reverts commit 73cf7963ff9a6dcb37b7713910ba81b797ffb743.

    * cleanup

    * Revert "ggml: pimp up dot graph"

    This reverts commit 6bc467133900e9ba8f5cf48710c9249ea7be8aaf.

    * less restrictive test
